  "texts": [
    "We show the generated post-surgery networks and residuals of three randomly selected subjects in Fig. 4.",
    "The connections within brain networks are highly heterogeneous in the context of a brain tumor.",
    "Herein, we imposed anatomical prior to act as a regularization method.",
    "However, a highly restrictive prior resulted in a complete loss of subject specificity despite FCNET achieving lower reconstruction errors.",
    "After some trials, we found that an optimal (or nearly optimal) prior was able to discard enough connections while still capturing some inter-subject variability of the networks (Fig. 4 red squares; see also Fig."
  ]
}